{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"226","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"沙國能源部長透露 OPEC明年可能放寬石油減產","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span heiti='' style='color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, helvetica, 微軟正黑體, Geneva, ' tc=''>沙烏地阿拉伯能源部長法里（Khalid al-Falih）透露，石油輸出國家組織（OPEC）與夥伴國，明年可能放鬆產量管制。國際油價聞訊上漲至近3週以來的高點。</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: center;'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/600_285.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 497px;' /><span heiti='' style='color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, helvetica, 微軟正黑體, Geneva, ' tc=''>沙烏地阿拉伯能源部長法里透露，石油輸出國家組織明年可能放鬆產量管制。</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: center;'><span heiti='' style='color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, helvetica, 微軟正黑體, Geneva, ' tc=''>（法新社資料照）</span></p>\n\n<h4 heiti='' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-weight: 600; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 22px; line-height: 25px; font-family: Arial, helvetica, 微軟正黑體, Geneva, ' tc=''>市場解讀將結束減產</h4>\n\n<p heiti='' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 30px; font-family: Arial, helvetica, 微軟正黑體, Geneva, ' tc=''>法里週六向媒體表示，沙烏地阿拉伯今年1月至3月原油產量遠低於產量上限，平均日產量約700萬桶；沙烏地阿拉伯希望OPEC及其盟國可以放寬生產限制，並在今年減產協議結束後，建立起永久適用於石油市場的框架。此話被市場解讀為將結束減產的訊息，刺激已在上週分別上漲3%、4%的西德州原油、布蘭特原油，進一步上漲至2月7日以來新高。</p>\n\n<h4 heiti='' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-weight: 600; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 22px; line-height: 25px; font-family: Arial, helvetica, 微軟正黑體, Geneva, ' tc=''>油價漲至近3週高點</h4>\n\n<p heiti='' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 30px; font-family: Arial, helvetica, 微軟正黑體, Geneva, ' tc=''>國際油價在漲至3週高點後，週一回復平穩。截至台灣時間週一傍晚，西德州原油期貨上漲0.09%、報每桶63.61美元，布蘭特原油期貨上漲0.04%、報67.34美元。</p>\n\n<p heiti='' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 30px; font-family: Arial, helvetica, 微軟正黑體, Geneva, ' tc=''>OPEC主席、阿拉伯聯合大公國能源部長馬茲勞埃（Suhail Al-Mazrouei）上週表示，OPEC成員國及非成員國如俄羅斯，為避免對市場造成重大衝擊，將在6月會議討論是否延長減產協議，法里的談話等於是提前釋出沙國希望放寬減產的訊息。</p>\n\n<p heiti='' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 30px; font-family: Arial, helvetica, 微軟正黑體, Geneva, ' tc=''>根據英國石油（BP）最新能源展望報告，因再生能源占全球能源供應比重將增加，估石油需求將在2030年代觸頂，較原先預期更快。另一方面，美國頁岩油生產成本漸降，今年產量料將持續增加，根據國際能源署（IEA）報告，美國原油日產量增84.6萬桶，即將超過沙烏地阿拉伯。</p>\n\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div heiti='' id='oneadIRTag' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: Arial, helvetica, 微軟正黑體, Geneva, ' tc=''>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div heiti='' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: Arial, helvetica, 微軟正黑體, Geneva, ' tc=''>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div heiti='' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: Arial, helvetica, 微軟正黑體, Geneva, ' tc=''>資料來源:http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/paper/1179534</div>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2018-03-05","clk_count":"193"}},"__N_SSG":true}